<L>__{interior united terminal, gate area seconds later}
<A>__{...and gets there just as the flight is boarding. jack looks through the crowd, spotting kate near the front of the line, about to hand her ticket to the gate attendant. he pushes through the throng of people, drawing some annoyed stares, finally making his way over to kate.}
<C>__{jack}
<P>__{(calling out)}
<D>__{kate!}
<A>__{kate turns and sees jack, a look of puzzlement on her face.}
