<D>__{we have two kids, annie and josh...}
<A>__{...kate looks at him, half mortified, half interested...}
<C>__{jack }
<D>__{...annies not much of a violin player but she tries really hard. shes a little precocious but thats only because she says whats on her mind. and when she smiles...}
<A>__{jack shakes his head, remembering, fighting back the tears...}
<C>__{jack }
<D>__{and josh...he has your eyes. he doesnt say much but we know hes smart...}
<P>__{(lost in the memory)}
<D>__{...hes always got his eyes open, always watching us... sometimes you can look at him and just know that hes learning something new... its like witnessing a miracle...}
<A>__{kates expression has sifted from annoyance to curiosity.}
<C>__{jack }
<D>__{...the house is a mess, but its ours...}
<P>__{(chuckling)}
<D>__{...well, after a hundred twenty two more payments it will be...}
